snippet.title: Plants vs Zombies Garden Warfare - Boss Mode Trailer Extended Version
snippet.description: In his never ending quest to defeat plants and obtain brains, Dr. Zomboss explains his greatest invention yet, Boss Mode! Watch the full length version of the Plants vs. Zombies Garden Warfare video that debuted at Gamescom '13.
